				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "This occurs after the player has refused to help the brothers and subsequently finds them dead/one of them dead. It can trigger in the swamp, teahouse or lair, and you may not know that Ethel is a hag at this point (depending on where it triggers). \r\nIn the first, you've met the brothers, in the second you skipped the confrontation and have no idea who these men are."
				}
